-------------------------------------------------------------------------
Features:
* As a user, I can login. 										1
* As an employee, I can add a car to the lot.					1
* As a customer, I can view the cars on the lot.				1
* As a customer, I can make an offer for a car.					1
* As an employee, I can accept or reject a 						1
		pending offer for a car.
* As the system, I update a car to an owned state 				1
		when an offer is accepted.
* As the system, I reject all other pending offers 				1
		for a car when an offer is accepted.
* As a user, I can register for a customer account. 			1
* As an employee, I can remove a car from the lot.				1
* As a customer, I can view the cars that I own.				1
* As a customer, I can view my remaining payments 				1
		for a car.
* As an employee, I can view all payments.						1
* As the system, I can calculate the monthly payment.			1
